<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>to be (am/is/are) – Hellweg-Realschule</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+2:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 60 40'><clipPath id='c'><path d='M0 0h60v40H0z'/></clipPath><rect width='60' height='40' fill='%23012169'/><g clip-path='url(%23c)'><path d='M0 0l60 40M60 0L0 40' stroke='white' stroke-width='8'/><path d='M0 0l60 40M60 0L0 40' stroke='%23C8102E' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M30 0v40M0 20h60' stroke='white' stroke-width='10'/><path d='M30 0v40M0 20h60' stroke='%23C8102E' stroke-width='6'/></g></svg>">
<style>
:root{--hr-blue:#b85c20;--hr-red:#C62828;--hr-green:#2e7d32;--hr-gray:#455A64;--ok:#2e7d32;--warn:#ef6c00;--bad:#b71c1c;}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;font-family:'Baloo 2',system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;background:#fef9f2;color:#2c1a0e;line-height:1.55;font-size:18px}
.container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 20px 96px}
header{text-align:center;padding:20px 10px 10px}
header img{height:70px;filter:drop-shadow(0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.15))}
header h1{margin:10px 0 0;font-size:clamp(26px,5vw,38px);color:var(--hr-blue);letter-spacing:.2px}
header p.sub{margin:6px 0 0;color:#7a5c3a}
.rules-combined{margin-top:14px;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#fdf2e3 0%,#fef5e4 40%,#f5f0ff 100%);border-radius:20px;box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(180,90,30,.12);padding:22px 20px 18px;border:1.5px solid #e8c99a}
.rules-combined h2{font-size:13px;color:#b85c20;margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.rc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px}
.rc-card{border-radius:14px;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;position:relative}
.rc-card.c-green{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f1f5fb,#f7f9fd);border:1.5px solid #d1dae8}
.rc-card.c-red{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f1f5fb,#f7f9fd);border:1.5px solid #d1dae8}
.rc-card.c-blue{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f1f5fb,#f7f9fd);border:1.5px solid #d1dae8}
.rc-card.c-indigo{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f1f5fb,#f7f9fd);border:1.5px solid #d1dae8}
.rc-card.c-amber{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f1f5fb,#f7f9fd);border:1.5px solid #d1dae8}
.rc-card.c-teal{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f1f5fb,#f7f9fd);border:1.5px solid #d1dae8}
.rc-card-full{display:none}
.rc-card-topbar{height:6px;width:100%;flex-shrink:0}.rc-card.c-green .rc-card-topbar{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#43a047,#66bb6a)}.rc-card.c-red .rc-card-topbar{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#e53935,#ec407a)}.rc-card.c-blue .rc-card-topbar{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#b85c20,#d4922e)}.rc-card.c-indigo .rc-card-topbar{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#3949ab,#7e57c2)}.rc-card.c-amber .rc-card-topbar{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#f9a825,#ffca28)}.rc-card.c-teal .rc-card-topbar{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#4a7c60,#6aa880)}.rc-card-body{padding:12px 14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;flex:1}.rc-card-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:900;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.7px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}.rc-card-num{position:absolute;top:6px;right:10px;font-size:52px;font-weight:900;line-height:1;opacity:.07;pointer-events:none;user-select:none}
.rc-card.c-green .rc-card-label{color:#1b5e20}
.rc-card.c-red .rc-card-label{color:#880e4f}
.rc-card.c-blue .rc-card-label{color:#8b4518}
.rc-card.c-indigo .rc-card-label{color:#1a237e}
.rc-card.c-amber .rc-card-label{color:#e65100}
.rc-card.c-teal .rc-card-label{color:#234d38}
.rc-formula{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;gap:6px 4px}.fc-pair{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0}
.fc{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:7px;padding:3px 7px;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0}
.fc-subj{background:#fde8c0;border:2px solid #d97520;color:#7a3010}
.fc-do{background:#fef9c3;border:2px solid #ca8a04;color:#713f12}
.fc-verb{background:#ecfeff;border:2px solid #0891b2;color:#164e63}
.fc-neg{background:#fee2e2;border:2px solid #ef4444;color:#7f1d1d}
.fc-sig{background:#f3e8ff;border:1.5px dashed #a855f7;color:#581c87;font-style:italic}
.fc-wh{background:#ffedd5;border:2px solid #f97316;color:#7c2d12}
.fc-punct{background:transparent;border:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:#7a5c3a;padding:0 2px}
.fc-short{background:#fff;border:2px solid #ffe082;color:#e65100;font-size:12px}
.fc-plus{font-size:11px;color:#90a4ae;font-weight:700;padding:0}
.fc-s{background:#d1fae5;border:2px solid #10b981;color:#065f46;font-size:12px}
.rc-rule{font-size:13px;color:#374151;line-height:1.55;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:9px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.rc-card.c-green .rc-rule{border-left:3px solid #a5d6a7;border-right:3px solid #a5d6a7;border-top:1px solid #a5d6a7;border-bottom:1px solid #a5d6a7}
.rc-card.c-red .rc-rule{border-left:3px solid #ef4444;border-right:3px solid #ef4444;border-top:1px solid #ef4444;border-bottom:1px solid #ef4444}
.rc-card.c-blue .rc-rule{border-left:3px solid #d97520;border-right:3px solid #d97520;border-top:1px solid #d97520;border-bottom:1px solid #d97520}
.rc-card.c-indigo .rc-rule{border-left:3px solid #6366f1;border-right:3px solid #6366f1;border-top:1px solid #6366f1;border-bottom:1px solid #6366f1}
.rc-card.c-amber .rc-rule{border-left:3px solid #ca8a04;border-right:3px solid #ca8a04;border-top:1px solid #ca8a04;border-bottom:1px solid #ca8a04}
.rc-card.c-teal .rc-rule{border-left:3px solid #0891b2;border-right:3px solid #0891b2;border-top:1px solid #0891b2;border-bottom:1px solid #0891b2}
.rc-examples-new{font-size:12.5px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.75;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.04)}
.rc-examples-new b{color:#140c04}
.hl-subj{color:#7a3010;font-weight:800;background:#fde8c0;border-radius:4px;padding:0 3px}
.hl-do{color:#713f12;font-weight:800;background:#fef9c3;border-radius:4px;padding:0 3px}
.hl-verb{color:#164e63;font-weight:800;background:#ecfeff;border-radius:4px;padding:0 3px}
.hl-neg{color:#7f1d1d;font-weight:800;background:#fee2e2;border-radius:4px;padding:0 3px}
.hl-sig{color:#581c87;font-weight:700;background:#f3e8ff;border-radius:4px;padding:0 3px}
.hl-wh{color:#7c2d12;font-weight:800;background:#ffedd5;border-radius:4px;padding:0 3px}
.hl-s{color:#065f46;font-weight:800;background:#d1fae5;border-radius:4px;padding:0 3px}
body.dark-mode .hl-subj{background:#3d2010;color:#93c5fd}
body.dark-mode .hl-do{background:#422006;color:#fde68a}
body.dark-mode .hl-verb{background:#3d2510;color:#a5f3fc}
body.dark-mode .hl-neg{background:#450a0a;color:#fca5a5}
body.dark-mode .hl-sig{background:#3d2510;color:#d8b4fe}
body.dark-mode .hl-wh{background:#431407;color:#fdba74}
body.dark-mode .hl-s{background:#1e1005;color:#6ee7b7}
.fc-tz{background:#dcfce7;border:1.5px solid #4a7c60;color:#234d38;border-radius:999px;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;font-size:11.5px}
body.dark-mode .rules-combined{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#0f1e38 0%,#111a30 50%,#2a1408 100%);border-color:#2a3a5e}
body.dark-mode .rules-combined h2{color:#e8a060}
body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-green,body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-red,body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-blue,body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-indigo,body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-amber,body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-teal{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e1408,#1e2840);border-color:#3d2510}
body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-green .rc-card-label{color:#a5d6a7}
body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-red .rc-card-label{color:#f48fb1}
body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-blue .rc-card-label{color:#fbbf77}
body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-indigo .rc-card-label{color:#c5cae9}
body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-amber .rc-card-label{color:#ffe082}
body.dark-mode .rc-card.c-teal .rc-card-label{color:#80cbc4}
body.dark-mode .fc-subj{background:#3d2010;border-color:#d97520;color:#93c5fd}
body.dark-mode .fc-do{background:#422006;border-color:#ca8a04;color:#fde68a}
body.dark-mode .fc-verb{background:#3d2510;border-color:#0891b2;color:#a5f3fc}
body.dark-mode .fc-neg{background:#450a0a;border-color:#ef4444;color:#fca5a5}
body.dark-mode .fc-sig{background:#3d2510;border-color:#a855f7;color:#d8b4fe}
body.dark-mode .fc-wh{background:#431407;border-color:#f97316;color:#fdba74}
body.dark-mode .fc-short{background:#2a1800;border-color:#f9a825;color:#ffe082}
body.dark-mode .fc-plus{color:#9a7050}
body.dark-mode .fc-punct{color:#b8905a}
body.dark-mode .fc-s{background:#1e1005;border-color:#10b981;color:#6ee7b7}
body.dark-mode .rc-rule{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);color:#c8b8a0}
body.dark-mode .rc-examples-new{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);color:#b8905a}
body.dark-mode .rc-examples-new b{color:#e8d0aa}
body.dark-mode .fc-tz{background:#1e3025;border-color:#6aa880;color:#a8d4bc}
.signal-box{display:none}
details.accordion{background:#fff;border-radius:16px;border:1px solid #e8d5b8;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.06);margin:16px 0;overflow:hidden}
details.accordion summary{list-style:none;cursor:pointer;padding:14px 18px;outline:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:#140c04;border-left:5px solid transparent;transition:background .2s}
.acc-num{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;font-size:13px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0}.acc-num-pair{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;flex-shrink:0}.acc-num-sub{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;background:#c5cae9;color:#1a237e}
#acc-aus .acc-num{background:#a5d6a7;color:#1b5e20}
#acc-kf .acc-num{background:#ffe082;color:#e65100}
#acc-vern .acc-num{background:#ffcdd2;color:#880e4f}
#acc-frag .acc-num{background:#fbbf77;color:#8b4518}
#acc-ka .acc-num{background:#c4b5fd;color:#5b21b6}
body.dark-mode .acc-num{opacity:.85}
body.dark-mode{background:#140c04;color:#e8d0aa}
body.dark-mode details.accordion{background:#1e1408;border-color:#3d2510}
body.dark-mode details.accordion summary{color:#e8d0aa}
body.dark-mode details.accordion[open] summary{border-bottom:1px solid #3d2510}
details.accordion[open] summary{border-bottom:1px solid #e8d5b8}
details.accordion summary:hover{filter:brightness(.97)}
#acc-aus summary{border-left-color:#2e7d32;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(170,200,160,.18),rgba(170,200,160,.04))}
#acc-kf summary{border-left-color:#d97706;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(251,191,36,.14),rgba(251,191,36,.03))}
#acc-vern summary{border-left-color:#C62828;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(198,40,40,.10),rgba(198,40,40,.02))}
#acc-frag summary{border-left-color:#b85c20;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(138,176,200,.18),rgba(138,176,200,.04))}
#acc-ka summary{border-left-color:#7c3aed;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(124,58,237,.12),rgba(124,58,237,.03))}
body.dark-mode #acc-aus summary{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(170,200,160,.10),rgba(170,200,160,.02))}
body.dark-mode #acc-kf summary{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(251,191,36,.08),rgba(251,191,36,.01))}
body.dark-mode #acc-vern summary{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(198,40,40,.07),rgba(198,40,40,.01))}
body.dark-mode #acc-frag summary{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(138,176,200,.10),rgba(138,176,200,.02))}
body.dark-mode #acc-ka summary{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(124,58,237,.08),rgba(124,58,237,.01))}
.content{padding:18px 20px}
.note{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fef5e4,#fef8f0);border:1px solid #f5c070;border-left:4px solid #b85c20;padding:11px 14px;border-radius:10px;margin:6px 0 16px;color:#3d2010;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}
.highlight{font-weight:600}
.level-switch{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin:10px 0 16px}
.level-switch button{border:2px solid #e8c99a;border-radius:999px;padding:8px 20px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;background:#fef5e4;color:#1e40af;transition:.2s all;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.2px;outline:none;position:relative}
.level-switch button:hover{background:#fde8c0;border-color:#d4922e;transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(21,101,192,.15)}
.level-switch button.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b85c20,#d4922e);color:#fff;border-color:transparent;box-shadow:0 3px 10px rgba(21,101,192,.4);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.task{border:1px solid #e8d5b8;border-top:3px solid #b8905a;background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:16px 18px;margin:12px 0;scroll-margin-top:80px;line-height:1.6;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.05);transition:box-shadow .2s}
#acc-aus .task{border-top-color:#2e7d32;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(170,200,160,.12),rgba(170,200,160,.05))}
#acc-kf .task{border-top-color:#d97706;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(251,191,36,.12),rgba(251,191,36,.05))}
#acc-vern .task{border-top-color:#C62828;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(198,40,40,.08),rgba(198,40,40,.02))}
#acc-frag .task{border-top-color:#b85c20;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(138,176,200,.12),rgba(138,176,200,.05))}
#acc-ka .task{border-top-color:#7c3aed;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(124,58,237,.08),rgba(124,58,237,.05))}
body.dark-mode .task{border-top-color:#3d2510;background:#1e1408;border-color:#3d2510}
body.dark-mode #acc-aus .task{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(170,200,160,.08),rgba(170,200,160,.02));border-top-color:#66bb6a}
body.dark-mode #acc-vern .task{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(198,40,40,.06),rgba(198,40,40,.01));border-top-color:#ef5350}
body.dark-mode #acc-frag .task{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(138,176,200,.08),rgba(138,176,200,.02));border-top-color:#64b5f6}
body.dark-mode .task .prompt{color:#e8d0aa}
body.dark-mode .task input[type="text"],body.dark-mode .task textarea{background:#140c04;color:#e8d0aa;border-color:#3d2510}
.task:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.09)}
.task.task--solved{border:2px solid #2e7d32;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(46,125,50,.15)}
.task.task--solved .task-solved-label{display:block}
.task-solved-label{display:none;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#2e7d32;margin-bottom:4px}
.task-type-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;border-radius:999px;padding:2px 10px;margin-bottom:6px}
.task-type-badge.badge-mc{background:#e0f2fe;color:#b85c20;border:1px solid #f5c070}
.task-type-badge.badge-ordne{background:#fef9c3;color:#854d0e;border:1px solid #fde047}
.task-type-badge.badge-frei{background:#f3e8ff;color:#7c3aed;border:1px solid #c4b5fd}
body.dark-mode .task-type-badge.badge-mc{background:#3d2510;color:#f5c070;border-color:#b85c20}
body.dark-mode .task-type-badge.badge-ordne{background:#422006;color:#fde68a;border-color:#ca8a04}
body.dark-mode .task-type-badge.badge-frei{background:#3d2510;color:#c4b5fd;border-color:#7c3aed}
body.dark-mode .task.task--solved{border-color:#66bb6a;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(102,187,106,.15)}
body.dark-mode .task-solved-label{color:#66bb6a}
.task.task--wrong{border-color:#f87171;border-top-color:#b91c1c;background:#fff5f5!important}
.task.task--wrong .prompt{color:#b91c1c}
body.dark-mode .task.task--wrong{border-color:#b91c1c;border-top-color:#f87171;background:#2a0f0f!important}
body.dark-mode .task.task--wrong .prompt{color:#f87171}
.task .prompt{margin:0 0 12px;font-weight:600;color:#140c04;line-height:1.6;font-size:15.5px}
.task input[type="text"]{width:100%;padding:11px 16px;border:2px solid #e8d0aa;border-radius:999px;font-size:16px;outline:none;transition:.2s all;box-sizing:border-box;background:#fef8f0;color:#140c04}
.task input[type="text"]:focus{border-color:#b85c20;background:#fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(21,101,192,.10)}
.task input[type="text"]:disabled{background:#f5ece0;color:#9a7050}
.task .controls{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
.btn{border:none;border-radius:999px;padding:9px 18px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;background:#e8d0aa;color:#3d2510;font-size:14px;transition:.15s all;letter-spacing:.1px}
.btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);filter:brightness(1.06)}
.btn:active{transform:translateY(0)}
.btn.primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#C62828,#e53935);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(198,40,40,.3)}
.btn.blue{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b85c20,#d4922e);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(21,101,192,.3)}
.btn.green{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2e7d32,#43a047);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(46,125,50,.3)}
.btn.gray{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#455A64,#9a7050);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(69,90,100,.2)}
.btn.ghost{background:#f5ece0;color:#7a5c3a;border:1px solid #e8d0aa}
.feedback{margin-top:8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 0;letter-spacing:.1px}
.solution{margin-top:8px;font-size:14px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0f9ff,#fef8f0);border:1px solid #bae6fd;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;display:none;line-height:1.65}
.hint-box{margin-top:8px;font-size:14px;background:#fffbeb;border:1px dashed #f59e0b;color:#92400e;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;display:none;line-height:1.55}
.ok{color:var(--ok)}.warn{color:var(--warn)}.bad{color:var(--bad)}
.mc-options{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;margin:4px 0 8px}
.mc-opt{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:#fef8f0;border:2px solid #e8d0aa;border-radius:12px;padding:10px 14px;cursor:pointer;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;transition:.15s all;color:#2c1a0e;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
.mc-opt:hover{background:#fef3e4;border-color:#93c5fd}
.mc-opt:active{transform:scale(.98)}
.mc-opt.mc-selected{border-color:#b85c20;background:#fde8c0;font-weight:700}
.mc-opt.mc-correct{border-color:#2e7d32;background:#dcfce7;color:#14532d}
.mc-opt.mc-wrong{border-color:#dc2626;background:#fef2f2;color:#991b1b;text-decoration:line-through;opacity:.7}
.mc-opt.mc-disabled{pointer-events:none;cursor:default}
.mc-letter{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:#e8d0aa;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;color:#7a5c3a}
.mc-opt.mc-selected .mc-letter{background:#b85c20;color:#fff}
.mc-opt.mc-correct .mc-letter{background:#2e7d32;color:#fff}
.mc-opt.mc-wrong .mc-letter{background:#dc2626;color:#fff}
body.dark-mode .mc-opt{background:#1e1408;border-color:#3d2510;color:#e8d0aa}
body.dark-mode .mc-opt:hover{background:#1e3050;border-color:#d97520}
body.dark-mode .mc-opt.mc-selected{background:#3d2010;border-color:#d97520}
body.dark-mode .mc-opt.mc-correct{background:#1e1005;border-color:#22c55e;color:#86efac}
body.dark-mode .mc-opt.mc-wrong{background:#450a0a;border-color:#ef4444;color:#fca5a5}
body.dark-mode .mc-letter{background:#3d2510;color:#b8905a}
.word-tiles-wrap{margin:4px 0 8px}
.word-tiles-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#b8905a;margin-bottom:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px}
.word-tiles{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;min-height:42px;padding:8px;border-radius:12px;background:#fef8f0;border:2px dashed #c8b8a0;transition:.2s all}
.word-tiles.wt-source{background:#f5ece0;border-color:#b8905a}
.word-tiles.wt-target{background:#fef3e4;border-color:#d97520;border-style:solid;min-height:46px}
.word-tiles.wt-target:empty::before{content:"Tippe die Wörter in der richtigen Reihenfolge an ↑";color:#b8905a;font-size:13px;font-style:italic;padding:6px}
.word-tile{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:10px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s all;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;user-select:none;border:2px solid #c8b8a0;background:#fff;color:#2c1a0e;box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.word-tile:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.12);border-color:#d4922e}
.word-tile:active{transform:scale(.95)}
.word-tile.wt-placed{background:#fde8c0;border-color:#d97520;color:#1e40af}
.word-tile.wt-used{opacity:.3;pointer-events:none;transform:scale(.9)}
.word-tile.wt-correct{background:#dcfce7;border-color:#22c55e;color:#14532d;pointer-events:none}
.word-tile.wt-wrong{background:#fef2f2;border-color:#ef4444;color:#991b1b;animation:wt-shake .4s}
@keyframes wt-shake{0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)}20%,60%{transform:translateX(-4px)}40%,80%{transform:translateX(4px)}}
body.dark-mode .word-tiles.wt-source{background:#140c04;border-color:#3d2510}
body.dark-mode .word-tiles.wt-target{background:#1e1408;border-color:#d97520}
body.dark-mode .word-tiles.wt-target:empty::before{color:#9a7050}
body.dark-mode .word-tile{background:#1e1408;border-color:#7a5c3a;color:#e8d0aa}
body.dark-mode .word-tile:hover{border-color:#e8a060}
body.dark-mode .word-tile.wt-placed{background:#3d2010;border-color:#d97520;color:#93c5fd}
body.dark-mode .word-tile.wt-used{opacity:.25}
body.dark-mode .word-tile.wt-correct{background:#1e1005;border-color:#22c55e;color:#86efac}
body.dark-mode .word-tile.wt-wrong{background:#450a0a;border-color:#ef4444;color:#fca5a5}
.section-actions{display:flex;gap:8px;margin:14px 0 10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.progress-wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin:12px 0 10px}
.progress{position:relative;width:260px;height:16px;background:#e8d0aa;border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;border:none;box-shadow:inset 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.1)}
.progress-fill{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:0%;background:#b85c20;transition:width .3s ease;border-radius:999px}
.progress.red .progress-fill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#C62828,#ef5350)}
.progress.green .progress-fill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#2e7d32,#43a047)}
.progress.mixed .progress-fill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#C62828 0%,#b85c20 100%)}
.progress-text{font-size:13.5px;color:#7a5c3a;font-weight:600}
.result-card{margin-top:14px;border:1px solid #e8d5b8;background:#fff;border-radius:16px;padding:14px;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.06)}
.score{font-size:22px;font-weight:800;margin:6px 0}
.celebrate-banner{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#dcfce7,#c7f0d8);border:2px solid #22c55e;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 14px;margin-bottom:12px;text-align:center;color:#14532d;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;animation:celebrate-pop .5s ease}
@keyframes celebrate-pop{0%{transform:scale(.8);opacity:0}50%{transform:scale(1.05)}100%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}}
.result-banner{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fef8f0,#fff);border:2px solid #b8905a;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:center;font-weight:700;color:#3d2010}
.result-banner.result-green{border-color:#22c55e;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#dcfce7,#f0fdf4);color:#14532d}
.result-banner.result-orange{border-color:#f97316;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffedd5,#fff7ed);color:#7c2d12}
.result-banner.result-red{border-color:#ef4444;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fee2e2,#fef2f2);color:#991b1b}
.error-list{margin-top:10px;padding:10px 14px;background:#fff5f5;border:1px dashed #dc2626;border-radius:10px;font-size:13px;color:#991b1b}
.error-list li{margin:4px 0}
body.dark-mode .celebrate-banner{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e3025,#1d3d2b);border-color:#22c55e;color:#a8d4bc}
body.dark-mode .result-banner{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e1408,#2a1d12);border-color:#b8905a;color:#e8d0aa}
body.dark-mode .result-banner.result-green{border-color:#22c55e;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e3025,#1d3d2b);color:#a8d4bc}
body.dark-mode .result-banner.result-orange{border-color:#f97316;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3410,#6b2f0b);color:#fbbf77}
body.dark-mode .result-banner.result-red{border-color:#ef4444;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#5f1414,#4a0f0f);color:#fca5a5}
body.dark-mode .error-list{background:#450a0a;border-color:#b91c1c;color:#fca5a5}
.dark-toggle{position:fixed;top:14px;right:16px;z-index:100;border:none;border-radius:999px;padding:8px 14px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;background:#b85c20;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.2);transition:.2s background,.2s transform}
.dark-toggle:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);background:#8b4518}
body.dark-mode .dark-toggle{background:#3d2510;color:#e8d0aa}
.tts-toggle{position:fixed;bottom:46px;left:16px;z-index:99;border:none;border-radius:999px;padding:7px 12px;font-weight:700;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;background:#fff;color:#b85c20;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.15);transition:.2s}
.tts-toggle:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
.tts-on{background:#b85c20;color:#fff}
.reset-all-btn{position:fixed;bottom:14px;left:16px;z-index:99;border:none;border-radius:999px;padding:7px 12px;font-weight:700;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;background:#fff;color:#b85c20;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.15);transition:.2s}
.reset-all-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
body.dark-mode .tts-toggle,body.dark-mode .reset-all-btn{background:#1e1408;color:#e8a060}
.quiz-divider{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin:22px 0 6px;padding:0 4px}
.quiz-divider::before,.quiz-divider::after{content:"";flex:1;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(184,92,32,.30),transparent)}
.quiz-divider span{font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#b85c20;white-space:nowrap;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
body.dark-mode .quiz-divider::before,body.dark-mode .quiz-divider::after{background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(220,140,60,.30),transparent)}
body.dark-mode .quiz-divider span{color:#e8a060}
#wwm-quiz{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#061840 0%,#030e2b 100%);border-radius:16px;border:1px solid rgba(255,204,0,.3);overflow:hidden}
#wwm-quiz>summary{color:#ffcc00;border-left-color:rgba(255,204,0,.8)!important;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,204,0,.12),rgba(255,204,0,.03))!important;font-size:17px}
#wwm-quiz>summary .acc-num{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b8860b,#daa520);color:#000}
.wwm-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 160px;gap:20px;align-items:start}
.wwm-ladder{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0a1e52,#061840);border:1px solid rgba(255,204,0,.3);border-radius:14px;padding:10px 8px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px}
.wwm-ladder-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:6px;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);border:1px solid transparent;transition:.2s all;cursor:default}
.wwm-ladder-row .wwm-qnum{width:18px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0;font-size:10px;opacity:.6}
.wwm-ladder-row .wwm-amount{flex:1;text-align:right;letter-spacing:.2px}
.wwm-ladder-row.milestone{color:rgba(255,204,0,.6);border-color:rgba(255,204,0,.2);background:rgba(255,204,0,.05)}
.wwm-ladder-row.done{color:rgba(100,220,120,.55)}
.wwm-ladder-row.current{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,204,0,.18),rgba(255,204,0,.08));border-color:rgba(255,204,0,.7);color:#ffcc00;box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(255,204,0,.25);font-size:12.5px}
.wwm-ladder-row.current .wwm-amount{text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,204,0,.6)}
.wwm-ladder-row.milestone.current{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,204,0,.28),rgba(255,204,0,.12))}
@media(max-width:640px){.wwm-ladder{display:none}.wwm-layout{display:block}}
.wwm-qbadge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d2a6e,#061840);border:2px solid rgba(255,204,0,.6);border-radius:999px;padding:4px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:#ffcc00;letter-spacing:.8px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,204,0,.2)}
#wwm-quiz .wwm-lifelines{display:flex;gap:8px;margin:10px 0 14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
#wwm-quiz .wwm-lifelines .chip{padding:6px 14px;border-radius:999px;border:2px solid rgba(255,204,0,.75);color:#ffcc00;background:radial-gradient(circle at 40% 35%,#1a3a8a,#061840);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.5px;font-size:12px;box-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(255,204,0,.2),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.1);text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,204,0,.4);cursor:pointer;transition:.2s all}
#wwm-quiz .wwm-lifelines .chip:hover:not(.chip-used){background:radial-gradient(circle at 40% 35%,#2a4faa,#0d2060);box-shadow:0 0 22px rgba(255,204,0,.45),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.15);transform:translateY(-2px) scale(1.05)}
#wwm-quiz .task,#wwm-quiz .wwm-stage{background:transparent;border:none;border-radius:0;box-shadow:none;padding:0;margin:0}
#wwm-quiz .task:hover,#wwm-quiz .wwm-stage:hover{box-shadow:none}
#wwm-quiz .task .prompt,#wwm-quiz .wwm-stage .prompt{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0f2d72 0%,#091e50 100%);color:#fff;border:2px solid #ffcc00;border-radius:16px;padding:18px 22px;text-align:center;font-weight:800;font-size:19px;box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(255,204,0,.12),0 6px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.5);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:14px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
#wwm-quiz .task .prompt::before,#wwm-quiz .wwm-stage .prompt::before{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%,rgba(255,204,0,.07),transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
#wwm-quiz .task .controls .btn.primary,#wwm-quiz .wwm-stage .controls .btn.primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f3080,#1a4db5);color:#ffecb3;border:1px solid rgba(255,204,0,.5);box-shadow:0 3px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.5),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.1)}
#wwm-quiz .task .controls .btn.green,#wwm-quiz .wwm-stage .controls .btn.green{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1b5e20,#2e7d32);color:#b9f6ca;border:1px solid rgba(0,230,118,.45);box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
#wwm-quiz .task .controls .btn.gray,#wwm-quiz .wwm-stage .controls .btn.gray{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e2a38,#2d3d50);color:#90a4ae;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15)}
#wwm-quiz .section-actions .btn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0c2a66,#163a8a);color:#ffecb3;border:1px solid rgba(255,204,0,.4);box-shadow:0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
#wwm-quiz .section-actions .btn:hover{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#163a8a,#1e4db5)}
#wwm-quiz .feedback{color:#ffecb3;font-size:15px;margin-top:10px}
#wwm-quiz .feedback.ok{color:#00e676;text-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,230,118,.5)}
#wwm-quiz .feedback.bad{color:#ff6b6b;text-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(255,80,80,.4)}
#wwm-quiz .feedback.warn{color:#ffcc00}
#wwm-quiz .controls .btn:focus{outline:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.9);outline-offset:3px;}
#wwm-quiz .controls .btn.green:focus{outline:2px solid #fff;outline-offset:3px;box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(255,255,255,.2),0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.4);}
.quiz-tip-box{margin-top:12px;padding:12px 16px;background:rgba(255,204,0,.08);border:1px solid rgba(255,204,0,.45);border-left:3px solid #ffcc00;border-radius:10px;color:#ffe082;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}
.quiz-explanation-box{margin-top:12px;padding:12px 16px;background:rgba(0,230,118,.07);border:1px solid rgba(0,230,118,.3);border-left:3px solid #00e676;border-radius:10px;color:#b9f6ca;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}
.quiz-streak{text-align:center;font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:#ffcc00;letter-spacing:.5px;min-height:32px;margin-bottom:10px;text-shadow:0 0 16px rgba(255,204,0,.7)}
#wwm-quiz .result-card{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#1a4faa 0%,#0d3080 50%,#071d55 100%);border:3px solid #ffcc00;box-shadow:0 0 60px rgba(255,204,0,.35),0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.7);color:#fff;border-radius:22px;overflow:hidden}
#wwm-quiz .score{color:#ffcc00}
#wwm-quiz{overflow:visible!important}
@keyframes quizFadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.quiz-question-enter{animation:quizFadeIn .45s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) forwards}
#wwm-quiz .wwm-lifelines .chip-used{opacity:.35;cursor:not-allowed;border-color:rgba(255,204,0,.25);color:rgba(255,204,0,.4);text-decoration:line-through;box-shadow:none}
.wwm-joker-options{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;margin-top:12px}
.wwm-option-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(10,30,90,.9),rgba(5,18,60,.9));border:2px solid rgba(255,204,0,.5);border-radius:999px;color:#fff;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;padding:10px 18px;text-align:left;transition:.2s all;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
.wwm-option-btn:hover{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(30,70,180,.9),rgba(15,45,130,.9));border-color:#ffcc00;box-shadow:0 0 16px rgba(255,204,0,.3);transform:scale(1.01)}
.wwm-opt-letter{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,204,0,.15);border:2px solid rgba(255,204,0,.6);color:#ffcc00;font-size:13px;font-weight:900;flex-shrink:0}
.wwm-phone-bubble{margin-top:14px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(5,20,60,.95),rgba(3,12,40,.95));border:2px solid rgba(100,180,255,.4);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 16px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.5),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
.wwm-phone-icon{font-size:32px;flex-shrink:0;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(100,180,255,.5))}
.wwm-phone-text{font-size:14px;color:#c5deff;line-height:1.7}
.wwm-phone-text b{color:#fbbf77}
.wwm-phone-text em{display:inline-block;margin-top:6px;font-style:normal;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border:1px solid rgba(100,180,255,.3);border-radius:8px;padding:4px 10px;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:15px}
.wwm-audience-box{margin-top:14px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(5,18,55,.95),rgba(3,10,36,.95));border:2px solid rgba(255,204,0,.35);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 16px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.wwm-audience-title{text-align:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#ffcc00;letter-spacing:.6px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,204,0,.4)}
.wwm-audience-bars{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center;height:110px}
.wwm-audience-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;flex:1;max-width:160px;height:100%}
.wwm-audience-pct{font-size:13px;font-weight:900;color:#ffcc00;min-height:18px}
.wwm-audience-bar{width:100%;min-height:4px;border-radius:6px 6px 0 0;cursor:pointer;transition:filter .2s}
.wwm-audience-bar:hover{filter:brightness(1.2)}
.wwm-audience-label{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);text-align:center;line-height:1.3;max-width:100%;word-break:break-word;margin-top:4px}
@media(max-width:600px){.level-switch button,.btn{padding:7px 13px;font-size:13px}.progress{width:160px}}
@media(max-width:900px){.rc-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:600px){.rc-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.rc-card-mid-left,.rc-card-mid-right,.rc-card-top,.rc-card-full{grid-column:auto;grid-row:auto}}
@media(max-width:600px){.dark-toggle{position:static;display:block;margin:0 auto 8px;box-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.15)}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<header>
<h1>to be (am / is / are)</h1>
<p class="sub">Klasse 5 – Unit 1</p>
</header>

<section class="rules-combined">
<h2>Regelkarten</h2>
<div class="rc-grid">

<div class="rc-card c-amber">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">Was bedeutet „to be“?</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">1</div>
<div class="rc-rule"><b>„To be“</b> bedeutet <b>sein</b> oder <b>sich befinden</b>. Es drückt aus, wie oder wer oder wo etwas oder jemand ist.</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
<b>Beispiele:</b><br>
<b><span class="hl-subj">I</span></b> am Tom. – Ich heiße Tom.<br>
<b><span class="hl-subj">She</span></b> is happy. – Sie ist glücklich.<br>
<b><span class="hl-subj">They</span></b> are in the classroom. – Sie sind im Klassenzimmer.
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="rc-card c-green">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">✅ Aussagesatz</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">2</div>
<div class="rc-rule">Alle 8 Pronomen einzeln mit ihrer Form von „to be“:</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
<b>Pronomen + Form:</b>
<div class="rc-formula"><span class="fc fc-subj">I</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">→</span><span class="fc fc-verb">am</span></span></div>
<div class="rc-formula"><span class="fc fc-subj">you</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">→</span><span class="fc fc-verb">are</span></span></div>
<div class="rc-formula"><span class="fc fc-subj">he</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">→</span><span class="fc fc-verb">is</span></span></div>
<div class="rc-formula"><span class="fc fc-subj">she</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">→</span><span class="fc fc-verb">is</span></span></div>
<div class="rc-formula"><span class="fc fc-subj">it</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">→</span><span class="fc fc-verb">is</span></span></div>
<div class="rc-formula"><span class="fc fc-subj">we</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">→</span><span class="fc fc-verb">are</span></span></div>
<div class="rc-formula"><span class="fc fc-subj">you</span> <span class="fc-short">(Plural)</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">→</span><span class="fc fc-verb">are</span></span></div>
<div class="rc-formula"><span class="fc fc-subj">they</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">→</span><span class="fc fc-verb">are</span></span></div>
</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new" style="margin-top:8px">
<b>Beispielsätze:</b><br>
<span class="hl-subj">I</span> <span class="hl-verb">am</span> ten years old.<br>
<span class="hl-subj">He</span> <span class="hl-verb">is</span> from England.<br>
<span class="hl-subj">We</span> <span class="hl-verb">are</span> in the classroom.
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="rc-card c-teal">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">Kurzformen (Contractions)</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">3</div>
<div class="rc-rule">Wir können die Pronomen + to be zusammenziehen:</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
<b>I am</b> → I'm<br>
<b>you are</b> → you're<br>
<b>he is</b> → he's<br>
<b>she is</b> → she's<br>
<b>it is</b> → it's<br>
<b>we are</b> → we're<br>
<b>you are</b> (Plural) → you're<br>
<b>they are</b> → they're
</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new" style="margin-top:8px">
<b>Beispiel:</b> <span class="hl-verb">I'm</span> happy. (Statt „I am happy“)
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="rc-card c-red">
<div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
<div class="rc-card-body">
<div class="rc-card-label">❌ Verneinung</div>
<div class="rc-card-num">4</div>
<div class="rc-rule">Für „nicht sein“ benutzen wir <b>am not / are not / is not</b>:</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new">
<b>I am not</b> (I'm not)<br>
<b>you are not</b> (you're not / you aren't)<br>
<b>he is not</b> (he's not / he isn't)<br>
<b>she is not</b> (she's not / she isn't)<br>
<b>it is not</b> (it's not / it isn't)<br>
<b>we are not</b> (we're not / we aren't)<br>
<b>you are not</b> (Plural) (you're not / you aren't)<br>
<b>they are not</b> (they're not / they aren't)
</div>
<div class="rc-examples-new" style="margin-top:8px">
<b>Beispiele:</b><br>
<span class="hl-neg">I'm not</span> sad. – Ich bin nicht traurig.<br>
